In his speech, Ouyang Yu first expressed warm congratulations and high esteem to the seven distinguished individuals who had been awarded honorary doctorates, who had made remarkable achievements in different fields and made outstanding contributions to the development of the country and the progress of the world. At the same time, Ouyang Yu expressed his most sincere wishes to the graduates and parents, and also paid a heartfelt tribute to the university's dedicated and academic staff team.
Sun Yifeng, Chair Professor of the Australasian College of Liberal Arts, read out Liu Zunyi's praise. He said that Professor Liu Zunyi is a globally renowned economist, known for his outstanding academic achievements and forward-looking educational philosophy.
